            <description><![CDATA[
<h2>What's New</h2>

<h3>Added</h3>
<ul>
<li>Token usage persistence with SwiftData for faster startup and historical tracking (macOS)</li>
<li>ClaudeMeterKit Swift Package for shared models across macOS, iOS, and widgets</li>
</ul>

<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Bump iOS deployment target to iOS 18.0</li>
<li>Refactor usage data models into shared ClaudeMeterKit package</li>
</ul>

<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Pin GitHub Action to commit hash for improved CI security</li>
</ul>

See <a href="https://github.com/tartinerlabs/ClaudeMeter/blob/main/CHANGELOG.md">CHANGELOG.md</a> for full details.
